{"meta":{"title":"彬","subtitle":"","description":"","author":"彬","url":"https://sosickbin.github.io","root":"/"},"pages":[{"title":"关于我","date":"2022-08-20T11:13:16.000Z","updated":"2023-06-28T06:13:47.000Z","comments":true,"path":"about/index.html","permalink":"https://sosickbin.github.io/about/index.html","excerpt":"","text":"———一些日常与文章———- 第三批00后，已经成长起来的一代人。 背景音乐: Luv (sic.) pt3"}],"posts":[{"title":"随笔","slug":"随笔","date":"2023-06-28T06:21:11.000Z","updated":"2023-06-28T06:35:37.170Z","comments":true,"path":"2023/06/28/随笔/","link":"","permalink":"https://sosickbin.github.io/2023/06/28/%E9%9A%8F%E7%AC%94/","excerpt":"","text":"2023博客新编博客很简陋，但旨在做一些日常与文章分享，而不是做技术，技术确实不咋地,算是一个网上笔记本。博客弄好到现在也有一年多快两年了，陆陆续续写了一些，但不够系统，没有主旨，所以删去了不少，我觉得系统的，有规律的把自己的想法记录下来，是一件不错的事。重点不在别人，而在于自己对自己的思想与观点变化的记录。以后可能会陆续发一些自己读的书(也包括听的,我也算喜马拉雅老用户了，哈哈)。","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"正式入门编程技能的概括","slug":"正式入门编程技能的概括","date":"2023-01-31T12:33:28.000Z","updated":"2023-06-28T06:49:24.562Z","comments":true,"path":"2023/01/31/正式入门编程技能的概括/","link":"","permalink":"https://sosickbin.github.io/2023/01/31/%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A8%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E7%9A%84%E6%A6%82%E6%8B%AC/","excerpt":"","text":"编程语言方面了解java语言 推荐《java核心技术》","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"宁的信","slug":"宁的信","date":"2022-08-06T13:55:45.000Z","updated":"2022-12-20T10:10:56.546Z","comments":true,"path":"2022/08/06/宁的信/","link":"","permalink":"https://sosickbin.github.io/2022/08/06/%E5%AE%81%E7%9A%84%E4%BF%A1/","excerpt":"","text":"2022 8.6 22:30 老家 写给宁","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"杂记","slug":"杂记","date":"2022-08-06T13:11:39.000Z","updated":"2023-06-28T06:25:59.016Z","comments":true,"path":"2022/08/06/杂记/","link":"","permalink":"https://sosickbin.github.io/2022/08/06/%E6%9D%82%E8%AE%B0/","excerpt":"","text":"2022 8.6 写在老家","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"c知识点","slug":"c语言","date":"2022-07-09T10:29:36.000Z","updated":"2023-06-28T06:49:25.871Z","comments":true,"path":"2022/07/09/c语言/","link":"